:<font size="15">שׁית</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
שׁית / shîyth / sheeth

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''שׁית'''

# to [[place]] (in a very wide application): - apply, appoint, array, bring, consider, lay (up), let alone, X look, make, mark, put (on), + regard, set, shew, be stayed, X take.

